<h3 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-Assumptions">Assumptions=
</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped relative-table confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 93.=
9178%;">
