ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Ref #</p></th>
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Assumption</p></th>
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7"><p>Description</p></th>
