A01</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
UETR is to be generated by channel, the format to be used is guid version 4=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Confirmed.&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A02</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
FX requirement is not currently in scope for this feature.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A03</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Hardcoded purpose/reason of payment need to be stored in COSMIC assume only=
 reason code is coming from the GPP file.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
No longer valid if the Purpose of payment description is coming from GPP fi=
le.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A04&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Some rules need to be built and positioned in the W1T Channel space:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>logic for currency / country cut-off</li>
<li>logic for extracting IBAN information and look up Bank detail&nbsp;</li=
>
<li>address lookup for beneficiary bank / intermediary bank&nbsp;</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
A06</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Logic for showing country specific fields for making a payment flow will=
 be handled in Channels, with Scenario index given from GPP file.&nbsp;</p>=
<p>Label for the branch identifier is assumed to be hardcoding in MFE. Assu=
me NCC rules file from GPP maintain the mappings of NCC and Country the lab=
el will be corresponding to a NCC.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
