lor: rgb(23,43,77);">D-ART-39663-003</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">Dependency</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Dependency on Sterling and EBIP on GPP files consumption and data normal=
isation.</p>
<p>And service support model needs to be defined in case of failure.&nbsp;<=
/p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">Sterling and EBIP</t=
d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2026-02-26" class=3D"date-past">26 Feb 2026</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">D-ART-39663-004</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">Dependency</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Dependency on Devops team to build the API for:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>EBIP to insert data into COSMIC</li>
<li>Channels to retrieve reference data (e.g. list of countries, list of cu=
rrencies) from COSMIC</li>
</ul>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062050" =
href=3D"/display/~M062050" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1515690289" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Andrew Suduk</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2026-02-26" class=3D"date-past">26 Feb 2026</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">D-ART-39663-005</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">Dependency</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>Dependency on the remaining open items from ACD, including whether payme=
nt limit will be in scope or not:<br><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-fil=
e-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image" draggable=3D"false" height=3D"196" src=3D"a58388580b9211d5c8178b80=
267b5e4e1e01324af1733da4f221c1d062ace624" data-image-src=3D"/download/attac=
hments/2289158549/image-2026-2-26_17-8-14.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationD=
ate=3D1772086095127&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-=
linked-resource-id=3D"2305578863" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-l=
inked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"im=
age-2026-2-26_17-8-14.png" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.=
com.au" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resourc=
e-container-id=3D"2289158549" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"50"=
 alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Updates:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>FX conversion is required for the Payment Limit use case. The Payment L=
imit is always calculated and enforced in AUD, regardless of the transactio=
n currency.</li>
<li>There is an outstanding design decision regarding the ownership of FX c=
onversion=E2=80=94specifically, whether it should be performed by the consu=
ming channel or by the Payment Limit API. At the time this Solution Design =
(SD) is being documented, the working assumption is that the Payment Limit =
API will be responsible for performing FX conversion whenever a non=E2=80=
=91AUD currency is provided.</li>
<li>This assumption will remain in effect unless superseded by a subsequent=
 architectural decision.</li>
</ul>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M058573" =
href=3D"/display/~M058573" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1125291984" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ave Cahyadi</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2026-02-26" class=3D"date-past">26 Feb 2026</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
