<h1 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-Solution"><span>Solution=
</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-SolutionOverview"><span>=
Solution Overview</span></h2>
<h3 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-MakeaPayment:">Make a Pa=
yment:</h3>
<p>New mappings are required as part of International payment related field=
s:</p>
<p><a href=3D"/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D2301121416">Make a payment UI=
 / API data mappings</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-Additionalfields:">Addit=
ional fields:</h4>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>International Beneficiary related fields are added to the payload, e.g.=
&nbsp;=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>creditor Address</li>
<li>beneficiary Address&nbsp;</li>
<li>creditor Agent</li>
<li>IBAN</li>
<li>UETR</li>
</ul></li>
<li>cut-off time for International payment based on country / currency. ( d=
isplay only on authorisation payment list and payment detail )</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<h4 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-Additionalinformationtob=
eretrievedduringmakeapaymentflow:">Additional information to be retrieved d=
uring make a payment flow:</h4>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Country list&nbsp;</li>
<li>Currency list&nbsp;</li>
<li>Purpose of payment list</li>
<li>Cut-off by country / currency</li>
<li>Bank detail by Swift / Bic</li>
<li>Bank detail by IBAN<strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"> (TBC)<=
/span></strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-FCATransfer:.1">FCA Tran=
sfer:</h3>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>No change is expected except currency is defaulted to the From Account =
currency <strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">(TBC)</span></strong>=
</li>
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Mapping=
s change refer to the below page:<br></span>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><a href=
=3D"/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D2301121416">Make a payment UI / API dat=
a mappings</a></span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"SD:InternationalPaymentOutward(Channels)-PaymentDetail:">Payment =
Detail:</h3>
<p>New fields are displayed on Payment detail screen and new attributes/map=
pings are expected:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>UETR</li>
<li>Beneficiary detail&nbsp;</li>
<li>Intermediary Bank detail</li>
<li><span data-teams=3D"true">Charge bearer</span></li>
<li><span data-teams=3D"true">Purpose of payment</span></li>
</ul>
