68da3220" alt=3D"" class=3D"gliffy-macro-image" width=3D"468" height=3D"196=
"></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table><strong> </strong>
<p></p>
<p><br></p>
